All boss battles teams are updated, often with more challenging pokemon with stronger movesets. More opponent pokemon now hold items. 
TMs are reusable
HMs are deleteable 
Starters are updated
Wild encounters are changed
Some moves are buffed.   
A few pokemon have their base stats buffed. For example - Feraligatr and arcanine's special attack and attack stats are reversed compared to the vanilla games. 
There is one pokemon with a type change
There are new TMs added  
Certain TMs previously only available in the post-game are now accessible earlier. 
